public class MultiInputManagerQuick
extends QuickBase<MultiInput>
A multi-input manager that makes various assumptions, so it can be more quickly specified.

    • getAdditionalChannels

      public List<ChannelEntry> getAdditionalChannels()
      Additional channels other than the main one, which are located in the main raster file

      If this list has at least one, then we treat the main raster file not as a stack, but break it into separate channels that are each presented as a separate stack to the MultiInput

    • setAdditionalChannels

      public void setAdditionalChannels​(List<ChannelEntry> additionalChannels)
      Additional channels other than the main one, which are located in the main raster file

      If this list has at least one, then we treat the main raster file not as a stack, but break it into separate channels that are each presented as a separate stack to the MultiInput
